px;\">\r\n									The voting platform will close on the 4th July 2017, and will then be followed by the official announcement at our 10th anniversary of &lsquo;Eduniversal World Convention&rsquo;, an annual conference for deans, directors and professionals in the Higher Education Industry.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									Your input will greatly contribute to the overall ranking of selected universities, and will be used when we conclude our final analysis of the 1000 Best Business Schools.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									You can complete this survey by simply clicking the link below:<br />\r\n									<a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/\" style=\"color: #0064e4\">http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com</a></p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									A tutorial is also on hand to help you navigate your way through the deans vote session:<br />\r\n									<a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/voting-tutorial\" style=\"color: #0064e4\">http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/voting-tutorial</a></p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									If you need assistance in completing the survey or if you have additional questions please contact us using the details below.</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- FOOTER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:540px;\">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"padding: 10px 10px 0 10px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #5d696e; margin-bottom: 0;\">\r\n					International Ranking Office</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"padding: 5px 15px 30px 15px;font-size: 14px\">\r\n				<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"flexible-center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; border