 mso-table-rspace:0pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"420\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td class=\"pd-top-0\" style=\"padding: 15px 10px;vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n								<p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 7px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n									EDUNIVERSAL EVALUATION SYSTEM</p>\r\n								<p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;\">\r\n									Dean&#39;s Vote Session 2017</p>\r\n								<p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n									<i>Adding a Peers Assessment Component</i></p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- /End HEADER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"pad-mobile\" style=\"padding: 20px 15px;\">\r\n				<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:540px;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style=\"font-size: 14px; padding-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									<span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">Dear Dean / Professor,</span></p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									We need your voice and we need it to be heard!</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									Do you believe that your &lsquo;industry know-how&rsquo; could contribute to the latest trends in higher education? Are you aware that your opinions and expertise, taken into account, could be shared on our platforms when our evaluation and university rankings are formed ?</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									The Eduniversal Ranking Agency is currently gathering information on a variety of topics centred around higher education, to be presented through brief interviews on our website and voiced by Professors and Deans from leading academic institutions. Participants may choose whether they prefer to answer through a video interview, or in written form.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									Interviewees will choose on what topic they wish to give their opinion on:</p>\r\n								<ul style=\"padding-left: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										The requirements necessary for campuses to thrive,</li>\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										Students and how will they change in the future,</li>\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										Youth entrepreneurship,</li>\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										School-business relationships,</li>\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										The era of digitalization and its impact on education,</li>\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										The biggest pedagogical challenges</li>\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										And finally, the role of deans with the students directly.</li>\r\n								</ul>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									The process to completing the interview is very straightforward: all of what is required for participants, is to simply login to their account profile as you did for the Deans Vote where you will find an &lsquo;Dean&#39;s Interview&rsquo; tab. A list of topics will then be presented to you, from which you can choose the topic you would like to address. After clicking on the question, you can write your answer directly into the comment section. Alternatively, if you prefer you can click on the video button to record your answers.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									You can save your work, and return to it at any time. Upon completion of your answer, simply validate the interview so that it can be sent to us and once it has been approved by our team, the interview will be shared online.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									We look forward to hearing and learning from you on these interesting subjects! If you wish to discuss the topic further or receive more information, please feel free to contact us.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									<br />\r\n									Kind regards,<br />\r\n									<br />\r\n									Cecile Escape<br />\r\n									Head of Ranking Office at Eduniversal Ranking Agency</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- FOOTER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:540px;\">\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"padding: 10px 10px 0 10px;\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #5d696e; margin-bottom: 0;\">\r\n					International Ranking Office</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"padding: 5px 15px 30px 15px;font-size: 14px\">\r\n				<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"flexible-center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; border-top: 1px solid #990098; \" width=\"280\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style=\"padding-top: 8px;\" width=\"30\">\r\n								<img alt=\"Email:\" src=\"http://eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/email.png\" /></td>\r\n							<td style=\"text-align: center; padding-top: 5px;\">\r\n								<a href=\"mailto:deans.vote@eduniversal.com\" style=\"color: #4a4a4a; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px;\"> deans.vote@eduniversal.com</a></td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style=\"padding-top: 8px;\" width=\"30\">\r\n								<img alt=\"Tel:\" src=\"http://eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/phone.png\" /></td>\r