le-rspace:0pt; text-align: left;\" width=\"420\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td class=\"pd-top-0\" style=\"padding: 15px 10px;vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n								<p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 7px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n									EDUNIVERSAL EVALUATION SYSTEM</p>\r\n								<p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold;\">\r\n									Dean&#39;s Vote Session 2017</p>\r\n								<p style=\"color: #fff; font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n									<i>Adding a Peers Assessment Component</i></p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- /End HEADER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"pad-mobile\" style=\"padding: 20px 15px;\">\r\n				<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:540px;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style=\"font-size: 14px; padding-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									<span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">Dear {title} {firstname} {lastname},</span></p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									As you may know every year, Eduniversal asks Deans from the best academic institutions worldwide for their expertise and opinion on the 1000 best Business Schools across 154 countries.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									We noticed that your institution participated in the 2016 Deans&rsquo; Vote and we would not want to miss the opportunity to, once again, take into account your vote and recommendations.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									Just to remind you, your recommendations will be weighted across three main criterias, which will be used by our ranking team when finalizing our rankings (<a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-ranking.com\">http://www.eduniversal-ranking.com</a>). This is why your involvement is greatly valued !</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									Click on the link below to access our Deans&#39; Vote platform :<br />\r\n									<a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com\">http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com</a></p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									A few weeks ago we sent out an email with login details for Deans to access the voting platform. If you are yet to vote, and still have not received the email, please send us a message and our team will be able to provide you with your personal login and password.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									Once you have logged in, you&rsquo;ll be presented with two options:</p>\r\n								<ul style=\"padding-left: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										Give us your latest opinion on the best 1000 best Business Schools, following the traditional voting procedure ;</li>\r\n									<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\r\n										Or, if your opinion hasn&rsquo;t changed since last year, simply re-submit your 2016 vote by clicking on the &laquo; <b>quick process</b> &raquo; button.</li>\r\n								</ul>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									We are slowly approaching the 2017 Deans Vote deadline on July 4th and would like to remind you to submit your votes as soon as possible.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									Furthermore, we would also like to to remind you that we are currently processing the Best Masters and MBA progam survey, which will be published on : <a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-survey-mastersranking.com\">http://www.eduniversal-survey-mastersranking.com</a></p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\r\n									As for the Deans&rsquo; Vote 2017, we slowly