lank\"> <img alt=\"Eduniversal Evaluation System (EES)\" src=\"{hostname}/static/default/images/email/header2018.jpg\" style=\"display: block; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px;\" /> </a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- /End HEADER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"pad-mobile\" style=\"padding: 20px 40px;\">\r\n				<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:500px;\">\r\n								&nbsp;</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style=\"font-size: 13px; padding-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 13px;\">\r\n									Dear <b>{title}</b> <b>{firstname}</b> <b>{lastname}</b>,</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n									Your school <b>{schoolname}</b> has been identified as one of the best academic institutions in your country by Eduniversal&#39;s official selection of the 1,000 Best Business Schools in 2017. As a Dean / Rector / Director of a 2017 ranked school, we welcome you to participate to a very unique survey in the world: the <strong>Eduniversal 2018 Deans&#39; Vote</strong>.<br />\r\n									&nbsp;</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #c115a5; text-decoration: underline\">\r\n									What is the Deans&rsquo; Vote about ?</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n									Each year, Eduniversal establishes a ranking of the 1,000 Best Business Schools, evaluating institutions in 154 different countries. These institutions are evaluated regarding a specific methodology, created by our Scientific Committee, which mainly takes into account internationalization criteria. However, in our ranking process, we also value your opinion as a Dean/Rector/Director of a ranked school. <strong>The Deans&rsquo; Vote is a peer-review process that aims at highlighting your expertise</strong>.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #c115a5; text-decoration: underline\">\r\n									Why participate in the Deans&rsquo; Vote ?</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									As an evaluation agency specialized in higher education, Eduniversal has a strong will to be in touch with the actual state of the institutions worldwide. By recommending academic institutions, from each geographical region, you contribute to build a more accurate picture of high education institutions in the Business field.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									And as a token of recognition, the results of this research will be published on Eduniversal&rsquo;s websites and announced officially during our <span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">11th &ldquo;Eduniversal World Convention&rdquo;</span>, an annual conference in the Higher Education Industry. Indeed, the recommendation rate from the Deans&rsquo; Vote directly <strong>helps to determine the position of each of the 1,000 schools</strong> among their own country and Palme League.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #ce9842; text-decoration: underline\">\r\n									The &ldquo;Eduniversal Selected Schools&rdquo; : give your opinion for the 2018 list!</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									Last year, <b>56,36%</b> of the voting Deans took part in the creation of a <b>new category of schools among our system</b> : the &quot;Eduniversal Selected&rdquo; schools. The goal of this project is <b>to identify promising schools</b> deserving to be presented as such to students worldwide. These schools are not included into the selection of the 1,000 Best Business Schools, and are not granted with a Palme of Excellence (they simply appear on our websites as institutions involved in a positive dynamic of development).</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									<b>Thus, we encourage you to give your opinion on the schools which, according to you, deserve to be identified as promising.</b> Your recommendations will provide important information to help the members of the Scientific Committee elaborate, areas by area and country by country, the 2018 list.&nbsp;If you are willing to participate to this research survey, it is very easy. For each country, the list of the concerned schools will be presented to you following the traditional Dean&rsquo;s Vote. You can confirm the schools of the 2017 Selected list, add schools which were already presented last year but did not enter the list, or directly nominate a new school.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #c115a5; text-decoration: underline\">\r\n									Are you ready to start voting?</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									You will find below your personal <span style=\"color: #990098; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">login and password</span> giving you access the &lsquo;2018 Deans&rsquo; Vote&rsquo; page:</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td align=\"center\" class=\"pad-mobile\">\r\n								<img alt=\"THE 2018 DEANS’ VOTE SESSION IS NOW OPEN\" src=\"{hostname}/static/default/images/email/ees-2018.png\" style=\"display: block; font-weight: bold; line-height: 30px;\" /></td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0; padding-top:5px;\">\r\n								<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:transparent; \" width=\"100%\">\r\n									<tbody>\r\n										<tr>\r\n											<td align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;vertical-align: top; \">\r\n												<div class=\"flexible-center\" style=\"width:240px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify;\">\r\n													<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;mso-tab