/> </a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- /End HEADER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"pad-mobile\" style=\"padding: 20px 20px;\">\r\n				<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:500px;\">\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style=\"font-size: 13px; padding-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 13px;\">\r\n									Dear <b>{title}</b> <b>{firstname}</b> <b>{lastname}</b>,</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n									Once again, Eduniversal is couting on your expertise for the Best 1,000 Business Schools Ranking in 154 Countries. In two days, you will receive the password and login allowing to activate your vote session on behalf of your institution so as to be able to participate in this survey.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									Since 2008, this survey is an important part of Eduniversal Evaluation System (EES).&nbsp;We thank all the deans who have volunteered their time each year for more than 10 years, so our methodology can be fully implemented<span style=\"color:#800080;\"><strong>*</strong></span>. In 2018, the participation rate reached <strong>70%</strong>.</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<img src=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/media-play-symbol.png\" style=\"width: 12px; margin-right: 5px;\" /> <a href=\"http://eduniversal-ranking.com/\" style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; color: #000;\" target=\"_blank\">Eduniversal Best Business Schools Ranking - Best Institutions in 154 countries</a></p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									Inside this ranking, the final rate of each schools is directly determined by the recognition of the peers. This year again, we need<strong> your institution&rsquo;s voice</strong> to accomplish what will be the 2019 Eduniversal ranking of the Best 1,000 Business Schools.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									<img src=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/media-play-symbol.png\" style=\"width: 12px; margin-right: 5px;\" /> <span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;\">Results of the 2019 Deans&rsquo; Vote</span> will be revealed during the <a href=\"http://convention.eduniversal.com/\" style=\"color: #9024a4; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">12<sup>th</sup> Eduniversal World Convention</a> in <span style=\"color: #9024a4; font-style: italic;\">Bangkok</span> - <b style=\"color: #9024a4; font-style: italic;\">Thailand</b> <span style=\"color: #9024a4; font-style: italic;\">from October 26 to 29, 2019</span>, hosted by <b>Sasin School of Management</b> (4 Palmes).</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									<img src=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/media-play-symbol.png\" style=\"width: 12px; margin-right: 5px;\" /> You can already <span style=\"font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">visit the voting platform</span> : <a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">DEANS&rsquo; VOTE 2019</a>, and prepare your voting session by downloading the list of the schools which will be submitted to this year recommendations:</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n									<span style=\"font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/document/2019-Eduniversal-Official-Selection-of-the-1000-Best-Business-Schools-in-154-countries.pdf\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #9024a4; font-size: 15px; display: inline-flex;\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/arrow-pointing-to-right.png\" style=\"width: 16px; margin-right: 5px;\" />2018 Official Selection </a> </span></p>\r\n								<p>\r\n								</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									<br />\r\n									<span style=\"color:#800080;\"><img src=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/question-mark.png\" style=\"width: 12px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></span><span style=\"color:#4b0082;\">For any question and more information, or if you have any request regarding the receipt of your institution&rsquo;s codes to access the voting platform, please directly write an email to</span> <a href=\"mailto:eva.urli@eduniversal-group.com \">eva.urli@eduniversal-group.com</a></p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									Sincerely yours,</p>\r\n								<p>\r\n									<b>Eduniversal Ranking Office</b></p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; text-align: justify;\">\r\n									<strong style=\"font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); color: rgb(128, 0, 128); text-align: justify;\">*</strong>According to the EES, the official representative of each of the 1,000 ranked schools (Dean/Rector/Director&hellip;) will receive by email a login details which will allow him/her, if he/she wishes to do so, to participate to this worldwide survey. The survey consists of a simple recommendation process: the 1,000 ranked schools&rsquo; representatives are invited to indicate which are the other ranked schools they would recommend to their staff or students.</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- begin FOOTER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:600px;\">\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0; color: #fff; padding: 60px 15px 0 15px; background-image: url(http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/static/default/images/email/bg-footer.png); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: top center; background-size: 100%;\">\r\n				<table align=\"left\" cellpaddi