ize: 20px; line-height: 30px;\" /> </a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<!-- /End HEADER -->\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"pad-mobile\" style=\"padding: 20px 20px;\">\r\n				<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size:0;line-height:0;min-width:500px;\">\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td style=\"font-size: 13px; padding-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 13px;\">\r\n									Dear <b>{title}</b> <b>{firstname}</b> <b>{lastname}</b>,</p>\r\n								<p style=\"font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n									Last year, our Ranking Office could not take advantage of your <b style=\"color: #6d2181;\">institution&rsquo;s expertise</b> in order to establish the <a href=\"http://eduniversal-ranking.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2018 Eduniversal Best 1,000 Business Schools ranking in 154 countries</a>. We missed with regret your recommendations which would have supported our analysis of the business education&rsquo;s situation all across the world.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									<b style=\"color: #6d2181;\">We would not miss again the opportunity to learn from your experience as Dean of one of the best business institution in the world</b> ; that is why we would like to <b>kindly remind you that this year Deans&rsquo; Vote survey is still open</b> and will be until <b style=\"color: red;\">July, 1st 2019</b>.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									As you may know, this annual survey allows Eduniversal to establish its annual ranking of the best Business Schools worldwide. Indeed, it invites the Deans of the Best Business Schools in the world to <b>recommend or to not recommend, country by country, their peers&rsquo; institutions</b>. It helps to paint a <i style=\"color: #6d2181;\">current portrait of the state of the business schools and of their global influence</i>.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n									It would be a privilege for us to enjoy your expertise in this matter.</p>\r\n								<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n									Your personal access to this year year survey is the following:</p>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0; padding-top: 0;\">\r\n								<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;background:transparent; \" width=\"100%\">\r\n									<tbody>\r\n										<tr>\r\n											<td align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;vertical-align: top; \">\r\n												<div class=\"flexible-center\" style=\"width:240px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify;\">\r\n													<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt; margin-bottom: 15px;  \" width=\"100%\">\r\n														<tbody>\r\n															<tr>\r\n																<td align=\"center\" class=\"pd-bot-5\" style=\"padding: 0 10px;vertical-align: middle; \">\r\n																	<p style=\"margin-bottom: 7px; font-size: 14px; color: #4f0e6a; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">\r\n																		Login:</p>\r\n																	<div style=\"border: 1px solid #923891; border-radius: 20px; display: block; font-size: 11px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; width: 180px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; padding: 4px 5px; margin: 0 auto; font-weight: bold;\">\r\n																		{email1}</div>\r\n																</td>\r\n															</tr>\r\n														</tbody>\r\n													</table>\r\n												</div>\r\n												<div class=\"flexible-center\" style=\"width:240px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; \">\r\n													<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-colla