ges/email/header_2019.png\" style=\"display: block; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px;\" /></a>\r\n					<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n						<a href=\"http://www.eduniversal-deans-vote.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td class=\"pad-mobile\" style=\"padding: 20px 20px;\">\r\n					<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n						<tbody>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td class=\"fix-gmail\" style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; min-width: 500px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style=\"font-size: 18px; padding-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n									<p style=\"color: rgb(109, 33, 129); padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\">\r\n										<b>&rarr; YOUR EXPERTISE AS HEAD OF ONE OF THE <span style=\"color:#800080;\">BEST INSTITUTIONS</span> WORLDWIDE <span style=\"color: #8E19BD\">MATTERS,</span><br />\r\n										<span style=\"color:#800080;\">MAKE IT</span><span style=\"color: #8E19BD\"> COUNTS&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&larr;</span></p>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style=\"font-size: 13px; padding-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n									<p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n										Dear <b>{title}</b> <b>{firstname}</b> <b>{lastname}</b>,</p>\r\n									<p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n										Every year, the Eduniversal Ranking Office relies on the <b style=\"color: #6d2181;\">expertise</b> and <b style=\"color: #6d2181;\">experience</b> of the best business institutions worldwide&rsquo;s Deans, Directors and Rectors to establish its annual Best 1,000 business schools ranking in 154 countries.</p>\r\n									<p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n										This year isn&rsquo;t an exception, and we opened the Deans&rsquo; Vote survey on April, 2019 in pursuing the goal to collect you and your peers&rsquo; expertise <b>about the today Higher Education world</b>.</p>\r\n									<p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n										To this date, we note with regrets that you have not yet participate <b>to this peers&rsquo; recognition process</b> ; that is why we would like to kindly remind you about it and give you some useful indications about this year voting session :</p>\r\n									<p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"color: #CB8C0F\">☆</span> The <b>survey platform</b> will remain open <b>until</b> <b style=\"color: #6d2181;\">July, 25th 2019</b> <span style=\"color: #CB8C0F\">☆</span></p>\r\n									<ul style=\"list-style: none;\">\r\n										<li>\r\n											<p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n												☆ The list of <b>the schools proposed to your analysis</b> during this year survey <b>is available <a href=\"{hostname}/static/document/2019-Eduniversal-Official-Selection-of-the-1000-Best-Business-Schools-in-154-countries.pdf\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #6d2181;\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></b> to upstream prepare your voting session and then <b>delegate the online</b> process to your PA ☆</p>\r\n										</li>\r\n										<li>\r\n											<p style=\"font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n												<span style=\"color: #CB8C0F\">☆</span> If you&rsquo;re short on time, you can also <b>decide to give your right to vote to a person from your team</b>, either by sharing with him/her your login details or by directly informing us by email <span style=\"color: #CB8C0F\">☆</span></p>\r\n											<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;background:transparent; \" width=\"100%\">\r\n												<tbody>\